You think you're safe in there?

535
00:44:05.560 --> 00:44:06.879
You're not safe.

536
00:44:06.880 --> 00:44:09.599
What no. "Hello Sean.
how are you doing mate?"

537
00:44:09.600 --> 00:44:12.079
I'm gonna make you pay
for what you've done.

538
00:44:12.080 --> 00:44:14.759
Listen. I'd love to sit and chat.

539
00:44:14.760 --> 00:44:18.520
hear you talk shit. but I've got
a court appearance to get ready for.

540
00:44:19.240 --> 00:44:21.359
Done!

541
00:44:21.360 --> 00:44:23.000
Recognise him?

542
00:44:26.280 --> 00:44:27.760
Should I?
Yeah.

543
00:44:28.800 --> 00:44:30.320
He helped you spike my drugs.

544
00:44:31.600 --> 00:44:33.239
You're losing it mate.

545
00:44:33.240 --> 00:44:35.520
The pressure's
getting to you. isn't it?

546
00:44:39.960 --> 00:44:41.800
My wife and son...

547
00:44:43.240 --> 00:44:46.159
...were killed in a hit and run
seven years ago.

548
00:44:46.160 --> 00:44:48.880
The driver vanished.
not a fucking trace.

549
00:44:51.200 --> 00:44:52.919
Until he rocks up last night.

550
00:44:52.920 --> 00:44:55.360
kills my driver.
and three of Faz's men.

551
00:44:57.440 --> 00:45:00.320
That was your wife?
So you do know him?

552
00:45:01.040 --> 00:45:03.399
Did you fucking hire him?
No.

553
00:45:03.400 --> 00:45:06.919
I recognise the face. that's all.

554
00:45:06.920 --> 00:45:08.600
Heard the chatter.

555
00:45:10.400 --> 00:45:12.000
He's a good bloke though.

556
00:45:13.360 --> 00:45:14.960
You think this is a joke?

557
00:45:15.800 --> 00:45:18.479
Hiring the hit and run driver
to spike those drugs?

558
00:45:18.480 --> 00:45:20.240
It wasn't a hit and run.

559
00:45:23.920 --> 00:45:26.240
Look. I heard...

560
00:45:26.920 --> 00:45:30.440
...he was paid
to crash into your wife.

561
00:45:31.240 --> 00:45:32.840
It was a targeted kill.

562
00:45:34.200 --> 00:45:35.920
That's the story on the street.

563
00:45:38.400 --> 00:45:40.280
What you didn't know that?

564
00:45:43.200 --> 00:45:44.520
You're fucking lying!

565
00:45:45.840 --> 00:45:47.159
Yeah. Fucking lying!

566
00:45:47.160 --> 00:45:49.959
Wait. what... What's his name?

567
00:45:49.960 --> 00:45:52.239
Who-Who paid him to do that?
I've got to go. Elliot.

568
00:45:52.240 --> 00:45:54.680
No. fucking sit...
Sean. wait! Wait! Wait.

569
00:45:57.960 --> 00:45:59.400
Tell me his name.

570
00:46:01.400 --> 00:46:02.960
You want me to tell you...

571
00:46:04.160 --> 00:46:07.400
...then beg. Beg me to tell you.

572
00:46:14.720 --> 00:46:16.600
Or don't.
OK.

573
00:46:21.200 --> 00:46:22.800
OK.

574
00:46:25.520 --> 00:46:27.879
I am begging you. Sean.
What's his name?

575
00:46:27.880 --> 00:46:30.679
No. I-I mean properly beg.

576
00:46:30.680 --> 00:46:32.560
Like you mean it.

577
00:46:37.640 --> 00:46:39.240
(SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC)

578
00:46:44.520 --> 00:46:46.120
Please.

579
00:46:48.120 --> 00:46:50.320
Please. Sean. tell me his name.

580
00:46:54.080 --> 00:46:55.519
Nah. I don't think so.

581
00:46:55.520 --> 00:46:56.679
Tell me!

582
00:46:56.680 --> 00:46:58.799
Goodbye. Elliot.
Sean. come back!

583
00:46:58.800 --> 00:47:01.399
Sean! Sean. come back here you worm!

584
00:47:01.400 --> 00:47:04.159
Hey. Calm down. Calm down.
Yeah. Yeah. Of course. Of course.

585
00:47:04.160 --> 00:47:06.919
Sean!
Tell me or I'll fucking kill you!

586
00:47:06.920 --> 00:47:08.919
That's it. Enough.
Sean!

587
00:47:08.920 --> 00:47:12.480
Enough.
SEAN!

